name: com.android.wallpaper.backup.MissingHashCodeGenerator
description: Generates hash codes for currently set static image wallpapers on N+ devices where they are missing because older versions of the app did not generate and set them. Static image wallpaper hash codes are necessary on N+ devices for the purposes of backup & restore because N+ WallpaperManager integer IDs are local to physical devices and not backed up and restored on the framework side.
